            </p>
        </a>
    </FloatingText>

    <FloatingText>
        <p class="floatText tracking-wide text-anti_atomic_8 dark:text-atomic_8">
            General Motors - Automotive
        </p>
    </FloatingText>
    <FloatingText>
        <a
            class="floatTextMoveL block mt-[10vh] max-w-md p-3 bg-anti_atomic_3 dark:bg-atomic_3 rounded-lg shadow mb-[20vh]"
        >
            <Icon
                name="simple-icons:generalmotors"
                class="pb-3 size-20 md:size-24 2xl:size-28 text-gray-50 dark:text-gray-800"
            />
            <p class="font-bold text-base tracking-normal text-slate-100 dark:text-slate-700">
                Software engineer in Infortainment system. Worked on automation
